name: Octies Galaxy
description: Octies Galaxy is a generative NFT collection on the TON platform, featuring a transparent economic model of the Octies infrastructure! Each character in the collection is created by its owner, making the collection even more valuable and unique. The NFTs in this collection are also valuable due to their utilities, which the user receives in the game “Octies.” Hurry up! Create your unique reptiloid and unlock its full potential! Visit our official channels for instructions and more information.
